de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure.item

Class Item<DataType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure.AbstractAdapterItem<DataType>
      • de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure.item.Item<DataType>
  • Type Parameters:
    DataType - The type of the item's data
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable, DataStructure, Filterable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<AbstractAdapterItem<DataType>>

    public class Item<DataType>
extends AbstractAdapterItem<DataType>
    A data structure, which holds the data of an item of an adapter. It has a state, a selection state and may be enabled or disabled.
    Since:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    Michael Rapp
